New features with AN-2007-12-22:

-	The program "lndir" has been added to the sources

-	The program "sgrow" has been added to the sources

-	mkisofs bug fix for multi extent files, make
	UDF part from multi extent files working again.
	Thanks to a hint from
	Pav Lucistnik <pav@oook.cz> <pav@FreeBSD.org>

-	cdrecord now fetches the media information again after
	formatting or blanking the medium to get correct size information.

-	libfind:find_main() now has a new enrironment parameter 
	to allow PATH to be imported from a shell that used libfind
	as builtin.

